text: (chaur changcha) now thngai del trong nung bramoulophdom puok anak now thngai bramoulophdom( daembi chomnoumchomreah) . noh kuchea thngai del sdeng chenhpi pheap khat bng ning pheap chamnenh . haey anaknea del mean chomnue leu a l laoh ning sang ampeula troemotrauv noh trong nung loubbambat pi ke nouv babakamm teanglay robsa ke ning banhchoul ke tow knong thansuokr del mean t ne l cheachraen haur pi kraom vea daoy puokke sthetnow knong noh chea amt . noh ku chea chokchy muoy da thom bamphot
